Seperti menunduk, bukan?

170
00:11:20,129 --> 00:11:23,440
Kelihatannya dia sedang berdoa.

171
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:25,769
Sepertinya begitu.

172
00:11:26,610 --> 00:11:28,710
Kukira dia kesepian.

173
00:11:28,710 --> 00:11:32,139
Tapi sekarang dia terlihat khusyuk.

174
00:11:51,659 --> 00:11:54,570
Mau istirahat?

175
00:11:55,470 --> 00:11:59,000
Anginnya sejuk, awannya cantik.

176
00:11:59,639 --> 00:12:02,039
Tempat ini indah sekali.

177
00:12:03,039 --> 00:12:04,509
Teruslah berjalan.

178
00:12:06,610 --> 00:12:09,820
Kita duduk sebentar. Aku lelah.

179
